{"tid":688960,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 戰神4攻略討論區 (2)","createTime":"2018-06-03T16:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T16:10:06.000Z","uid":188318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a99479e92938637563779661e0d34ccb449f81d6","tid":688960,"uid":188318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T16:46:59.000Z","msg":"《戰神》<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/004656_cfbeb5a2b43b6fab3862781e047d159b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F004656_cfbeb5a2b43b6fab3862781e047d159b.png&h=ab90c212&s={SIZE}\" />（英語：God of War，又譯作「戰神4」是聖塔莫尼卡工作室開發並由索尼互動娛樂發行到PlayStation 4平台上的動作冒險遊戲，同時也是繼《戰神：崛起》後的系列（英語：God of War (franchise)）第八部作品以及2010年《戰神III》的續作。該作將以北歐神話為核心設定，與之前以希臘神話為根基的七部作品大為不同。系列主人公克雷多斯（英語：Kratos (God of War)）會繼續擔任主角，並擁有一個名叫阿特柔斯的兒子。作為他兒子的導師和保護者，克雷多斯已經學會控制一直驅使他行動的怒氣。遊戲於2018年4月20日發售。"},{"pid":"be3939870be44311c970532be490a7c7f930cad7","tid":688960,"uid":20325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打哂三條龍但唔見左粒龍涙，有咩方法</blockquote>巴德爾條龍果粒執咗未?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有唔同位執?唔係一打完果堆野就有?"},{"pid":"a2dfd07a51fd12ef354a0e10a8bdba19c5dd0b53","tid":688960,"uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"之前kuso戰神條友出左part two<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連把聲都好似"},{"pid":"ccc155f7987151e926d2434ea63fa16b642ed1f3","tid":688960,"uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2dfd07a51fd12ef354a0e10a8bdba19c5dd0b53","tid":688960,"uid":45017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"之前kuso戰神條友出左part two<br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連把聲都好似"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:13:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SCYxJ7gc_rs\" data-sr-url=\"